platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Dandara is full of fascinating movement. Everything from weapon effects to subtle background details are beautifully animated. Swipe to launch yourself from platform to platform, and with practice, darting past obstacles while blasting enemies can be achieved with almost poetic precision. Impressive level design offers thrilling, almost puzzle-like combat and hides plenty of secrets for more patient adventurers to pursue. This is not an easy game, but for those willing to learn its intricacies, Dandara is immensely rewarding.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Ready for a challenge? Leap into this fascinating, unforgiving adventure.
